# Monorepo Boundaries

- `apps/web` is the coach dashboard.
- `apps/mobile` is the client companion app.
- `packages/shared` holds shared product types and contracts.
- `packages/supabase-client` holds shared Supabase client helpers and generated database types.
- Put cross-app domain logic in shared packages when it is truly reused; avoid copy-pasting logic between web and mobile.
- Do not move app-specific UI, routing, or platform behavior into shared packages.
- When changing shared contracts, think through impact on both web and mobile before editing.
